  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<p><img src="/media/13099187/eurostar-snow-7-838x330-hero.jpg" alt="snowtrainhero" data-udi="umb://media/a108b997dac543acb7afc0de16fe7cd6" /></p>
</div>
<p>In time for this ski season, Eurostar have brought back the much anticipated ski train - carrying passengers from London to Bourg-Saint-Maurice throughout the peak ski season of December to February. To celebrate the return of the ski train, Inghams have created a unique, hassle free ski package for your next winter holiday, including travel on the Eurostar Snow train. </p>
<ul>
<li>Enjoy the ease of travel by train - from London to Bourg-Saint-Maurice</li>
<li>Spend an extra day on the slopes with a 7 day ski pass</li>
<li>Transfers included to resorts across Tignes, Val d'Isere and Les Arcs</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>See our <a data-udi="umb://document/2bf29261e6e747a98423e8b40c1d21ea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2bf29261e6e747a98423e8b40c1d21ea}" title="EuroStar Snow Train" data-anchor="#">Eurostar Snow Train Guide</a> for all the details of this great way to travel this 2023/24 ski season. </strong></p>
<p>Book your Inghams ski holiday with the Eurostar Snow train package:</p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
<h3>Included in your package: </h3>
<p>Here is an example itinerary of your Eurostar Snow train adventure as part of your Inghams ski holiday package. </p>
<p><strong>Outbound journey</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The Eurostar Snow train departs St Pancras at 9am</li>
<li>You will change platform in Lille at 11:30am</li>
<li>You will depart Lille at 12:15pm</li>
<li>Arriving in Bourg-St-Maurice at 18:20pm</li>
<li>There are then transfers to Tignes and Val D’Isere. For Les Arcs, guests will funicular to resort</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Inbound journey</strong> </p>
<ul>
<li>Extra ski day on the last Saturday – 7th day included for the price of 6 (including lift pass and ski equipment)</li>
<li>Tignes/Val D’Isere guests will transfer to Base Camp Lodge Hotel. Les Arcs guests by funicular to Base Camp Lodge</li>
<li>Dinner at Base Camp Lodge</li>
<li>Sunday morning shuttle from the hotel to the train station</li>
<li>The Eurostar Snow train departs at 08:11am</li>
<li>You will arrive in Lille at 14:30pm</li>
<li>You will then depart Lille at 15:30pm</li>
<li>Arriving back at St Pancras at 15:57pm</li>
</ul>
<h2>Find out more:</h2>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4>Call to book this offer</h4>
<p id="WhyChoose"><img src="/media/13099200/eurostar-12-500x500.jpg" alt="calltobook" data-udi="umb://media/1f16e02a1a1d4220a6567e9d7466f3c2" /></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div></div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4>Discover more</h4>
<p><img src="/media/13099202/eurostar-snow-11-500x500.jpg" alt="discovereurostar" data-udi="umb://media/8bf6f5a63db448a7998a262aee814ee0" /></p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.eurostar.com/uk-en/train/france/ski-train" target="_blank" class="c-btn">Eurostar Snow Train</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div></div>
</div>
<div class="data-grid">
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span>16 December 2023 to 4 February 2024</span></li>
<li>
<p>2nd class train travel between London St Pancras and Bourg-St-Maurice stations (times shown are provisional and could change).</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Return minibus transfers to Val d’Isère/Tignes or funicular and bus ticket to Les Arcs.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>8 nights’ accommodation with 7 nights in your chosen resort and the last night at Base Camp Lodge in Bourg-St-Maurice in twin/triple/quad room on a half-board basis.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Minibus transfer to railway station for the return train.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Ski pack offers (7 days for the price of 6 on lift passes and equipment hire) are only available if pre-booked.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Train supplements may apply.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>There is no Inghams rep based in Bourg-St-Maurice but available by phone if needed.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>All guests will need to check-out of their ski resort accommodation on Saturday morning where luggage can be stored with a transfer to Bourg late afternoon after the extra day skiing.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>]]></bodyText>
